{"tid":214022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夠啦你班連登仔 班女仔已經好慘 唔好再係咁炒興PTGF件事好無?","createTime":"2017-04-23T13:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T14:29:08.000Z","uid":68084,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1b9f7033028e8ad0fce81f58afb6a77883ebe8","tid":214022,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"我真係覺得個班做PTGF既女仔好慘<br />\n<br />\n出黎搵錢都要比你地公審<br />\n<br />\n有錢邊個想下海丫<br />\n<br />\n笑貧不笑娼<br />\n<br />\n佢地都係求財<br />\n<br />\n只不過係手法衰D<br />\n<br />\n又簡客<br />\n<br />\n又懶清高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我單左黎睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都比我見到一個識既女仔<br />\n<br />\n原本以為自己會好驚訝<br />\n<br />\n點知睇到之後好平淡<br />\n<br />\n我係到諗 可能人地屋企有困難<br />\n<br />\n逼不得已先出黎做姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我對佢都唔會話特別反感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反你地班連登仔<br />\n<br />\n係到不斷踩低班女仔<br />\n<br />\n話佢地係臭雞<br />\n<br />\n咁做真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n你地隨時搞到人地嫁唔出或跳樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n<br />\n對連登好失望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面有D痕痕地<br />\n<br />\n唔知1000蚊夠唔夠呢<br />\n<br />\nWTS個女仔問下先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa263b9a1f12e5fce760ba5bb87857675beb5d10","tid":214022,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7db3bf31939088ba3f675e3592dba09224854df","tid":214022,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bde2089ac859ccfdb29423c43fdd90f171c644","tid":214022,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891ce9b